        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;flowchart TD\n    RK4[RK4 Integrator]\n\n    Parent[TennesseeEastmanModel / DynamicModel Pai]\n\n    Layout[StateLayout / StateRegistry]\n    Plan[EvaluationPlan / ExecutionGraph]\n\n    State[Estado hipotético de avaliação]\n    Derivs[Derivadas yp]\n\n    subgraph Components[Componentes do domínio]\n        V1[Valve]\n        A1[Agitator]\n        D1[Disturbance]\n        R1[Reactor]\n        S1[Separator]\n        C1[Compressor]\n        ST1[Stripper]\n        SEN[Sensor]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Exposure[Camada de exposição]\n        PI[Process Image]\n        OPC[OPC-UA Adapter]\n        MOD[Modbus Adapter]\n        MA[4-20 mA Adapter]\n    end\n\n    RK4 --&gt;|passa estado hipotético| State\n    RK4 --&gt;|chama evaluate_derivatives| Parent\n\n    Parent --&gt; Layout\n    Parent --&gt; Plan\n    Parent --&gt; Components\n\n    State --&gt; Parent\n    Components --&gt; Parent\n    Parent --&gt; Derivs\n    Derivs --&gt; RK4\n\n    Parent --&gt;|após step consolidado| SEN\n    SEN --&gt; PI\n    PI --&gt; OPC\n    PI --&gt; MOD\n    PI --&gt; MA&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="9O6AmFjlwTHNbXbObUb2-36">
